<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Ngama</author>
<hymn_number>73</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ei hilh zo thei ding mi kuo a um dem?
 Sun leh zan in tamtak ka dawng ta a;
 Gen thiem leh thei chu tamtak a um,
 Mahleh a gen zothei chu a um puou.

[V2]
 Thagau thiengtho, Nang in ei hung hilh in,
 A pienna bawng In leh A thihna Kalvari;
 Leimi suihlung mawl te'n,
 Joar ei Tunpa hi,
 Gen zo thei a um puou,
 Hin khawpi ka tun lawh.

[V3]
 2. Bethlehem ah van bungpi a kek hi,
 Suohlam mi leh Belampute puipa;
 Si-al lien, kei le ei hung puiin,
 Muh ka nuom, van Lalcha a sielnau chu.

[V4]
 3. A pien in leng Herod gal a hung lien,
 Thah guon Judaten thimthu a lel ui;
 Ka gitloh leibat dit di'n Lalpa,
 Gitloh ziekin A thii khawpi pam ah.

[V5]
 4. Mi cheng chengin hung en diu Lalpa khuh,
 Jerusalem nu-nauhaw dinmun ah;
 Hansedawl thing chungah a khai ui,
 Thasietna luonthi a luong lo thei puoi.</lyrics>
<title>A Pienna Bawng In</title>
</song>